{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-25-2",
 "title": "Grounded on Dreven",
 "summary": "Pushing the Triton deep into Imperial space toward the capital world of Dreven, the disguised intelligence team -- Bazil McKenzie as the swooper Mege Vauki, Kathryn as the singer Mersche, and the slicer Marcus as Bazil's \"brother\" Marcus Vauki -- arrives amid a vast Imperial fleet and is ordered to land for inspection. On the spaceport landing field they are confronted by the armored Imperial commander Zeak, who grounds their ship and surrounds it with stormtroopers and a suspiciously heavy KDY technical team. Maintaining their cover as harmless cargo haulers with a faulty grav stabilizer, the trio spins a casual story of aimless prospecting while Bazil hides their weapons. Zeak impounds the Triton \"for repairs\" on the Emperor's orders, confiscates their weapons, and confines them from the ship, all while gently fishing for information about their travels.",
